data.name: Urine Bags
data.description:
## TYPES
- Economic Type
- Standard Type
- Luxus Type
- With Volutrol
- Leg Urine Bags
- Pediatric Urine Bags

## FEATURES
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile
- Clear, flexible, kink-resistant inlet PVC tubing
- Tubes in different lengths available
- Non-reflux valve
- Clear graduation in ml
- Non-drip slide taps
- Latex-free
- Ridged universal connector
- Ridged inlet
- Inlet cap
- Tubing
- Clamp
- Hanger
- Graduation scale
- Outlet
- Non-return valve
- Ventilation
